cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image analysis and machine learning techniques for histopathology images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) domains. The use of fully convolutional networks (FCN) and objectness prior interaction (OPI) also suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Additionally, the use of histopathology images suggests a potential focus on medical imaging (cs.MM) as well.
